%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Diversionary%20Tactic'%3A%20AIADMK's%20Palaniswami%20on%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20Sanatana%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06112837%2FF5Q66tyX0AArZmF.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20after%20Tamil%20Nadu%20sports%20and%20youth%20welfare%20minister%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20remark%20on%20%3Cem%3Esanatana%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%20erupted%20into%20a%20controversy%2C%20AIADMK%20general%20secretary%20Edappadi%20Palaniswami%20commented%20that%20the%20DMK%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20a%20talking%20point%20only%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20other%20issues%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Coimbatore%20on%20Tuesday%2C%205%20September%2C%20Palaniswami%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20law-and-order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20has%20deteriorated.%20The%20state%20is%20now%20seeing%20easy%20availability%20of%20drugs%20to%20the%20youngsters%2C%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20price%20of%20essential%20commodities%2C%20and%20a%20hike%20in%20property%20tax%2C%20and%20thereby%20people%20are%20suffering%20under%20the%20DMK%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20divert%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20from%20all%20these%20issues%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20has%20staged%20a%20drama%20called%20the%20abolition%20of%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEPS%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20contested%20the%20Presidential%20election%2C%20the%20DMK%2C%20which%20now%20speaks%20about%20the%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%20voted%20against%20him%20and%20even%20against%20current%20President%20Droupadi%20Murumu.%20The%20DMK%20even%20abused%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20Speaker%20P%20Dhanapal%20and%20DMK%20organising%20secretary%20RS%20Bharathi%20and%20also%20talked%20ill%20about%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20Dalit%20judge.%20This%20is%20the%20dharma%20of%20the%20DMK.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20AIADMK%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20Palaniswami%20said%20that%20his%20party%20was%20beyond%20the%20factors%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Udhayanidhi%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20nepotism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20told%20reporters%20in%20Chennai%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20AIADMK%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9CSanathana%20Dharma%20issue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20reporters%20asked%20Palaniswami%20about%20it%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20general%20secretary%20said%20that%20Udhayanidhi%20was%20trying%20to%20boost%20himself%20and%20the%20news%20media%20was%20helping%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20he%20done%20as%20a%20minister%3F%20Except%20for%20being%20the%20grandson%20of%20Karunanidhi%20and%20the%20son%20of%20Stalin%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20qualifications.%20He%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20nepotism%20which%20is%20high%20in%20the%20DMK%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20EPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20a%20DMK%20cadre%20become%20a%20chief%20minister%20or%20leader%20of%20the%20party%3F%20Even%20DMK%20ministers%20say%20that%20they%20will%20accept%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20son%20as%20their%20leader%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20pitiful%20state%20of%20the%20DMK.%20The%20DMK%20is%20not%20a%20party.%20It%20is%20a%20corporate%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20Stalin%20afraid%20of%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20M.K.%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9COne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%9D%20stand%2C%20Palaniswami%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CStalin%20claims%20he%20is%20the%20best%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20entire%20country.%20Then%2C%20why%20is%20he%20afraid%20of%20elections%3F%20Let%20him%20face%20the%20people%20and%20election%20again%20and%20prove%20his%20claim.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CTamil%20Nadu%20is%20the%20state%20that%20has%20the%20highest%20debt.%20This%20is%20the%20only%20achievement%20of%20Stalin%20in%20his%20two-and-a-half%20years%E2%80%99%20tenure.%20People%20will%20teach%20the%20DMK%20a%20lesson%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20for%20upholding%20dynastic%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20465px)%2085vw%2C%20465px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22465%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n.jpeg%20890w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649645%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22465%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEdappadi%20K.%20Palaniswami.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FEdappadi%20K.%20Palaniswami%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20262%20eminent%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20including%20former%20high%20court%20judges%20and%20bureaucrats%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20on%20Tuesday%20urging%20him%20to%20take%20note%20of%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20speech%20calling%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20concern%20over%20the%20growing%20incidents%20of%20hate%20speeches%2C%20the%20bureaucrats%20urged%20the%20apex%20court%20to%20take%20a%20suo%20moto%20notice%20of%20contempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThus%2C%20cases%20should%20be%20suo%20moto%20registered%20and%20the%20offenders%20should%20be%20proceeded%20against%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%20Any%20hesitation%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20directions%20would%20be%20viewed%20as%20contempt%20of%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20since%20the%20state%20government%20has%20refused%20to%20take%20action%20and%20acted%20in%20contempt%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20orders%20and%20gravely%20undermined%20or%20rather%20made%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20we%20urge%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20take%20the%20suo%20moto%20notice%20of%20contempt%2C%20ensuring%20accountability%20for%20the%20inaction%20of%20the%20state%20government%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20take%20decisive%20steps%20to%20prevent%20the%20inducement%20of%20hate%20speech%2C%20preserving%20public%20order%20and%20peace%20and%20we%20request%20you%20to%20take%20immediate%20appropriate%20actions%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20took%20to%20X%20to%20say%20that%20he%20had%20sought%20permission%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20to%20prosecute%20Udhayanidhi%20for%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20TN%20Governor%20seeking%20Sanction%20to%20Prosecute%20Stalin%20beta%20who%20on%20nepotism%20is%20a%20Minister.%20Once%20more%20if%20he%20repeats%20deprecating%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20I%20will%20work%20for%20dismissal%20of%20TN%20State%20Government.%20I%20proved%20in%201991%20that%20India%20is%20a%20Union%20of%20States%2C%20not%20a%20Federation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20have%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20TN%20Governor%20seeking%20Sanction%20to%20Prosecute%20Stalin%20beta%20who%20on%20nepotism%20is%20a%20Minister.%20Once%20more%20if%20he%20repeats%20deprecating%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20I%20will%20work%20for%20dismissal%20of%20TN%20State%20Government.%20I%20proved%20in%201991%20that%20India%20is%20a%20Union%20of%20States%20not%20a%20Federation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20(%40Swamy39)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSwamy39%2Fstatus%2F1698999046596141441%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwamy%2C%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Governor%2C%20stated%20that%20Udhayanidhi%20was%20creating%20an%20environment%20of%20fear%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20believers%20and%20was%20inciting%20violence%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20connection%2C%20I%20intend%20to%20initiate%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20against%20the%20above-named%20person.%20The%20accused%20is%20a%20public%20figure%20having%20major%20public%20outreach%2C%20following%2C%20and%20viewership.%20The%20offending%20statement%20made%20by%20the%20Accused%20has%20successfully%20reached%20millions%20of%20people%20and%20has%20influenced%20countless%20persons%2C%20creating%20an%20environment%20of%20fear%20in%20the%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20community%2C%20even%20more%20so%2C%20since%20the%20political%20party%20of%20the%20Accused%20is%20the%20ruling%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20statements%20of%20the%20accused%20have%20created%20a%20traumatising%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%2C%20alarm%2C%20threat%2C%20insecurity%2C%20and%20helplessness%20among%20believers%20of%20the%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20especially%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20Swamy%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20stereotyping%20of%20a%20particular%20section%20of%20the%20population%20and%20stigmatising%20it%20has%20created%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20hatred%20which%20is%20intended%20to%20generate%20aggression%20and%20incite%20violence%20and%20riots%20against%20them.%20For%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20said%20complaint%2C%20your%20sanction%20is%20required%20under%20Section%20196%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%201973%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20kind%20attention%20is%20drawn%20to%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20vs.%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20(2012)%20where%20the%20court%20has%20expounded%20principles%20governing%20the%20grant%20of%20sanction%20for%20prosecution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swami%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20it%20is%20requested%20that%20you%20may%20kindly%20accord%20for%20the%20prosecution%20for%20the%20accused%20who%20has%20committed%20various%20offences%20against%20public%20tranquillity%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20justice%2C%20and%20the%20exercise%20of%20your%20constitutional%20prerogative%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Swamy%20seeking%20sanction%20to%20prosecute%20Udhayanidhi%20his%20controversial%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%F0%9D%97%9F%F0%9D%97%B2%F0%9D%98%81%F0%9D%98%81%F0%9D%97%B2%F0%9D%97%BF%20%F0%9D%98%81%F0%9D%97%BC%20%F0%9D%97%9B%F0%9D%97%BC%F0%9D%97%BB%E2%80%99%F0%9D%97%AF%F0%9D%97%B9%F0%9D%97%B2%20%F0%9D%97%A7%F0%9D%97%A1%20%F0%9D%97%9A%F0%9D%97%BC%F0%9D%98%83%F0%9D%97%B2%F0%9D%97%BF%F0%9D%97%BB%F0%9D%97%BC%F0%9D%97%BF%20%F0%9D%98%80%F0%9D%97%B2%F0%9D%97%B2%F0%9D%97%B8%F0%9D%97%B6%F0%9D%97%BB%F0%9D%97%B4%20%F0%9D%97%A6%F0%9D%97%AE%F0%9D%97%BB%F0%9D%97%B0%F0%9D%98%81%F0%9D%97%B6%F0%9D%97%BC%F0%9D%97%BB%20%F0%9D%98%81%F0%9D%97%BC%20%F0%9D%97%A3%F0%9D%97%BF%F0%9D%97%BC%F0%9D%98%80%F0%9D%97%B2%F0%9D%97%B0%F0%9D%98%82%F0%9D%98%81%F0%9D%97%B2%20%F0%9D%97%A8%F0%9D%97%B1%F0%9D%97%B5%F0%9D%97%AE%F0%9D%98%86%F0%9D%97%AE%F0%9D%97%BB%F0%9D%97%B6%F0%9D%97%B1%F0%9D%97%B5%F0%9D%97%B6%20%F0%9D%97%A6%F0%9D%98%81%F0%9D%97%AE%F0%9D%97%B9%F0%9D%97%B6%F0%9D%97%BB%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F