20seer%20has%20set%20a%20price%20for%20my%20head.%20I%20ask%20you%2C%20whoever%20says%20this%20is%20a%20saint%3F%20Why%20you%20are%20so%20fond%20of%20my%20head%3F%20You%20are%20a%20seer%3B%20how%20can%20a%20sage%20have%20%E2%82%B91%20crore%3F%20Is%20he%20a%20real%20seer%3F%20Why%20%E2%82%B910%20crore%20to%20chop%20my%20head%3F%20If%20you%20give%20me%20a%20%E2%82%B910%20for%20a%20comb%2C%20I%20myself%20can%20comb%20my%20hair%2C%E2%80%9D%20Udhayanidhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Ftamilnadu%2Faiadmk-breaks-silence-on-udhayanidhi-stalins-sanatana-remark-diversionary-tactic-says-palaniswami%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20South%20First.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693980939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06112837%2FF5Q66tyX0AArZmF.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdiversionary-tactic-aiadmks-palaniswami-on-udhayanidhi-stalins-sanatana-remark%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AIADMK%20general%20secretary%20Edappadi%20Palaniswami%20claimed%20that%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20was%20trying%20to%20boost%20himself%20and%20the%20news%20media%20was%20helping%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdiversionary-tactic-aiadmks-palaniswami-on-udhayanidhi-stalins-sanatana-remark%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20violence%3A%20SC%20to%20hear%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India's%20plea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693979961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103419015%2Cimgsize-56626.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur-violence-editors-guild-of-india-seeks-protection-against-arrest-supreme-court-to-hear-plea%2Farticleshow%2F103418897.cms%22%2C%22sum