rbiter%20photographs%20India's%20Moon%20lander%20Vikram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693978106000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FDD67%2Fproduction%2F_130997665_nasaimage.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66725852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nasa%20said%20its%20Lunar%20Reconnaissance%20Orbiter%20took%20the%20image%20four%20days%20after%20India's%20historic%20Moon%20landing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66725852%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66725852.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66725852.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Be%20Called%20Bharat%3F%20Renaming%20Controversy%20Explained%20In%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20has%20also%20been%20used%20in%20a%20G20%20booklet%20meant%20for%20foreign%20delegates%20titled%20-%20%26quot%3BBharat%2C%20The%20Mother%20Of%20Democracy%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBharat%20is%20the%20official%20name%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Constitution%20as%20also%20in%20the%20discussions%20of%201946-48%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20booklet%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpresident-draupadi-murmus-g20-dinner-invite-sparks-buzz-republic-of-bharat-4360671%5C%22%3Emarks%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20nomenclature%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20international%20stage%20as%20the%20country%20prepares%20to%20host%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20other%20top%20world%20leaders.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Sambit%20Patra%20last%20night%20also%20shared%20a%20document%20on%20the%20PM's%20visit%20to%20Indonesia%20that%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20of%20Bharat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESources%20say%C2%A0the%20government%20may%20put%20forward%C2%A0a%20resolution%20to%20change%20the%20country's%20name%20later%20this%20month%20in%20the%20five-day%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20that%20starts%20on%20September%2018.%C2%A0The%20fact%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20announced%20any%20agenda%20for%20the%20special%20session%20has%20only%20added%20to%20the%20speculation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20drew%20scathing%20criticism%20from%20the%20Opposition.%20The%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20accused%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Bdistorting%20history%20and%20dividing%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Congress%20Chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20called%20a%20meeting%20of%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20alliance%20to%20discuss%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20linked%20the%20government%20move%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20their%20alliance.%C2%A0AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20asked%20whether%20the%20ruling%20party%20would%20change%20the%20country's%20name%20to%20'BJP'%20if%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20decided%20to%20call%20itself%20'Bharat'.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20no%20one%20has%20the%20right%20to%20change%20the%20country's%20name.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20understand%20why%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20perturbed%20over%20a%20name%C2%A0(INDIA%20bloc)%20related%20to%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NCP%20chief%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBJP%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20welcomed%20the%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20nomenclature%20and%20accused%20the%20Opposition%C2%A0of%20being%20anti-national%20and%20anti-constitutional.%20They%20said%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20in%20Article%201%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BIndia%2C%20that%20is%20Bharat%2C%20shall%20be%20a%20Union%20of%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnion%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20use%20'Bharat'%20is%20a%20big%20statement%20against%20the%20colonial%20mindset.%20%26quot%3BThis%20should%20have%20happened%20earlier.%20It%20gives%20me%20great%20satisfaction.%20'Bharat'%20is%20our%20introduction%20and%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20it.%20The%20President%20has%20given%20priority%20to%20'Bharat'%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20just%20two%20days%20after%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%2C%20suggested%20that%20the%20country%20discard%20India%20and%20switch%20to%20Bharat.%26quot%3BWe%20must%20stop%20using%20the%20word%20India%20and%20start%20using%20Bharat.The%20name%20of%20the%20country%20Bharat%20will%20remain%20Bharat%20wherever%20you%20go%20in%20the%20world.%20In%20spoken%20and%20written%20one%20must%20say%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693977840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fmgu1m9io_draupadi-murmu-pm-modi-twitter-650_650x400_21_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-over-india-india-name-change-g20-invites-india-to-be-called-bharat-renaming-controversy-explained-in-10-points-4363628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20use%20of%20'President%20of%20Bharat'%20-%20instead%20of%20the%20traditional%20'President%20of%20India'%20-%20on%20official%20G20%20Summit%20invitations%20has%20sparked%20a%20buzz.%20The%20move%2C%20that%20comes%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20has%20sent%20political%20temperatures%20soaring.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-over-india-india-name-change-g20-invites-india-to-be-called-bharat-renaming-controversy-explained-i