ia-66725416.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20On%20'India-Bharat'%20Debate%20Amid%20Rumours%20Of%20Name%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20veiled%20dig%20at%20Opposition%20parties%20over%20their%20comments%20following%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20sending%20out%20invitations%20for%20a%20G20%20dinner%20on%20September%209%20on%20behalf%20of%20'President%20of%20Bharat'%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20India%20that%20is%20Bharat%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20connotation%20of%20the%20word%20'Bharat'%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20that%20is%20Bharat%2C%20it%20is%20there%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20Please%2C%20I%20would%20invite%20everybody%20to%20read%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20opposition%20parties'%20reaction%20and%20if%20the%20government%20is%20going%20to%20reposition%20India%20as%20Bharat%20coinciding%20with%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20when%20you%20say%20Bharat%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20a%20meaning%20and%20understanding%20and%20a%20connotation%20that%20comes%20with%20it%20and%20that%20is%20reflected%20in%20our%20Constitution%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20was%20resorting%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrama%26quot%3B%20just%20because%20they%20got%20together%20and%20called%20their%20bloc%20as%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20have%20strongly%20supported%20the%20move%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20posted%20on%20'X'%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20dinner%20invite%20to%20him%20from%20the%20President%20and%20wrote%20a%20few%20lines%20from%20the%20national%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20should%20have%20happened%20earlier.%20This%20gives%20great%20satisfaction%20to%20the%20mind.%20'Bharat'%20is%20our%20introduction.%20We%20are%20proud%20of%20it.%20The%20President%20has%20given%20priority%20to%20'Bharat'.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20statement%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20colonial%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20made%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20news%20is%20indeed%20true.%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20has%20sent%20out%20an%20invite%20for%20a%20G20%20dinner%20on%20September%209th%20in%20the%20name%20of%20'President%20of%20Bharat'%20instead%20of%20the%20usual%20'President%20of%20India'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Article%201%20in%20the%20Constitution%20can%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BBharat%2C%20that%20was%20India%2C%20shall%20be%20a%20Union%20of%20States.%26quot%3B%20But%20now%20even%20this%20%26quot%3BUnion%20of%20States%26quot%3B%20is%20under%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20'X'%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20trying%20to%20distort%20history%20and%20said%20'BHARAT%26quot%3B%20is%20objective%20of%20INDIA%20parties.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20BHARAT-Bring%20Harmony%2C%20Amity%2C%20Reconciliation%20And%20Trust.%20Judega%20BHARAT%20Jeetega%20INDIA!%2C%26quot%3B%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20government's%20efforts%20to%20hold%20G20%20events%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20said%20it%20is%20essential%20that%20today's%20India%20develops%20sharper%20global%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferent%20cities%2C%20different%20states%2C%20different%20professions%20and%20generations%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20participation%20and%20ownership.%20And%20this%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20the%20G20.%20It%20is%20a%20larger%20mindset.%20It%20could%20be%