%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20was%20asked%20if%20President%20Putin%20and%20President%20Xi%20not%20being%20present%20will%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20New%20Delhi%20G20%20Summit%20being%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20think%20it%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20India.%20I.%20I%20think%20whatever%20decision%20they%20make%2C%20they%20would%20know%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20in%20response%20to%20another%20query.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20attend%20the%2018th%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20It%20gave%20no%20reason%20for%20Xi%20Jinping's%20absence%20from%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Putin%2C%20in%20a%20telephone%20conversation%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20month%2C%20had%20conveyed%20his%20inability%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20informed%20that%20Russia%20would%20be%20represented%20by%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergey%20Lavrov.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20issues%20being%20taken%20up%20are%20not%20new.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20put%20it%20this%20way%2C%20the%20issues%20are%20there.%20These%20are%20not%20issues%20that%20are%20this%20morning%20being%20taken%20up%2C%20I%20mean%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20gestation%20period%20of%20eight-nine%20months%2C%20where%20at%20different%20levels%20ministers%20or%20officials%20have%20tried%20to%20progress%20an%20issue.%20So%2C%20this%20is%20like%20a%20culmination.%20These%20are%20really%20about%2016-18%20processes%20which%20are%20all%20coming%20together%20to%20be%20stitched%20up%20together%20to%20produce%20a%20summit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20we%20are%20negotiating%20ri