0vs%20Sri%20Lanka%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20match%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20thriller%20on%20Tuesday.%20Sri%20Lanka%20secured%20a%20win%20while%20managing%20to%20defend%20a%20total%20of%20291%20runs%20against%20a%20spirited%20Afghanistan%20side%20that%20tried%20to%20get%20to%20the%20target%20under%2037%20overs.%20The%20end%20result%20was%20Afghanistan%20getting%20bowled%20out%20for%20289%20in%2037.4%20overs.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20match%2C%20a%20controversy%20over%20the%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20struck%2C%20with%20the%20Afghans%20claiming%20that%20they%20were%20not%20informed%20of%20the%20exact%20calculations%20by%20the%20match%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20tried%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20of%20292%20runs%20in%2037.1%20overs%20which%20would've%20given%20them%20the%20edge%2C%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20NRR%20of%20Sri%20Lanka.%20But%2C%20what%20they%20were%20not%20aware%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20had%20a%20chance%20of%20qualifying%20for%20the%20Super-4%20stage%20even%20after%20they%20had%20failed%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20of%20292%20runs%20in%2037.1%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%2037%20overs%20concluded%2C%20Afghanistan%20were%20289%20for%208.%20The%20qualification%20condition%20meant%20that%20they%20had%20to%20score%20three%20runs%20off%20one%20ball%20to%20win%20while%20bettering%20Sri%20Lanka's%20NRR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20bowling%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dhananjaya%20de%20Silva%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F50705-dhananjaya-maduranga-de-silva-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDhananjaya%20de%20Silva%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mujeeb%20ur%20Rahman%20went%20for%20a%20big%20hit%20and%20was%20caught%20on%20the%20long-on%20boundary.%20Non-striker%20Rashid%20Khan%C2%A0sank%20to%20his%20knees%2C%20thinking%20Afghanistan's%20journey%20in%20the%20tournament%20was%20over.%20But%2C%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20later%20learned%20that%20Afghanistan%20would've%20finished%20