s%20formed%20in%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20become%20a%20major%20hurricane%20as%20it%20approaches%20the%20Caribbean%20by%20the%20weekend.%20Currently%20located%20east%20of%20the%20Lesser%20Antilles%2C%20the%20storm%20is%20forecast%20to%20strengthen%20and%20pass%20just%20northeast%20of%20the%20Caribbean%20region.%20The%20National%20Hurricane%20Center%20has%20warned%20that%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20determine%20the%20exact%20impact%20on%20the%20Leeward%20Islands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftropical-storm-lee-forms-in-atlantic-forecast-to-become-major-hurricane-heading-to-the-caribbean%2Farticleshow%2F103414678.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftropical-storm-lee-forms-in-atlantic-forecast-to-become-major-hurricane-heading-to-the-caribbean%2Famp_articleshow%2F103414678.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftropical-storm-lee-forms-in-atlantic-forecast-to-become-major-hurricane-heading-to-the-caribbean%2Famp_articleshow%2F103414678.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%204%20Lakh%20Indians%20Will%20Die%20Waiting%20For%20US%20Green%20Card%2C%20Says%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%204%20lakh%20Indians%20will%20die%20before%20they%20receive%20a%20green%20card%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20over%2011%20lakh%20applications%20from%20Indians%20are%20pending%20in%20US's%20employment-based%20green%20card%20backlog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20green%20card%20or%20a%20Permanent%20Resident%20Card%20is%20a%20document%20issued%20to%20US%20immigrants%20granting%20them%20permanent%20residence%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20makes%20up%2063%25%20of%20the%20total%2018%20lakh%20employment-based%20green-card%20applications%20now%20pending%20in%20the%20country%2C%20US-based%20think%20tank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cato.org%2Fblog%2F18-million-employment-based-green-card-backlog%5C%22%3ECato%20Institute%20said%20in%20its%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20backlog%20adds%20to%20the%2083%20lakh%20pending%20applications%20from%20the%20family-sponsored%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20for%20new%20applicants%20from%20India%2C%20the%20backlog%20is%20effectively%20%26quot%3Ba%20life%20sentence%26quot%3B%20with%20over%20134%20years%20of%20wait%20time.%20%26quot%3BAbout%20424%2C000%20employment-based%20applicants%20will%20die%20waiting%2C%20and%20over%2090%20percent%20of%20them%20will%20be%20Indians.%20Given%20that%20Indians%20are%20currently%20half%20of%20all%20new%20employer-sponsored%20applicants%2C%20roughly%20half%20of%20all%20newly%20sponsored%20immigrants%20will%20die%20before%20they%20receive%20a%20green%20card%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20US%20employs%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20Indians%20and%20Chinese%20for%20STEM%20roles%2C%20only%20seven%20per%20cent%20of%20employment-based%20green%20cards%20can%20go%20to%20individuals%20from%20a%20country%20annually.%20This%20puts%20Indian%20at%20a%20significant%20disadvantage%20with%20over%20half%20of%20the%20backlog%20for%20employees%20of%20US%20businesses%20with%20advanced%20degrees%20including%20highly-skilled%20STEM%20professionals%20and%20US-educated%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20green%20card%20wait%20time%20has%20become%20a%20slow-brewing%20crisis%20in%20the%20US%20which%20has%20now%20left%20Indian%20applicants%20in%20a%20constant%20state%20of%20limbo%20despite%20efforts%20by%20the%20current%20Biden%20administration%20and%20initiatives%20by%20Indian-American%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20astounding%20backlogs%20and%20massive%20waits%20underscore%20that%20legal%20immigration%20to%20the%20United%20States%20is%20nearly%20impossible.%20Even%20to%20get%20to%20the%20point%20of%20entering%20the%20backlog%20takes%20an%20enormous%20amount%20of%20good%20fortune%2C%20and%20the%20lucky%20few%20that%20make%20it%20through%20the%20labyrinth%20face%20the%20daunting%20prospect%20of%20never%20actually%20receiving%20green%20cards%20in%20decades%20or%20even%20their%20lifetimes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693971900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fqrel1o0o_green-card-representational_625x300_02_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fover-4-lakh-indians-will-die-waiting-for-us-green-card-says-study-4363584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%204%20lakh%20Indians%20will%20die%20before%20they%20receive%20a%20green%20card%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20over%2011%20lakh%20applications%20from%20Indians%20are%20pending%20in%20US's%20employment-based%20green%20card%20backlog.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fover-4-lakh-indians-will-die-waiting-for-us-green-card-says-study-4363584%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fover-4-lakh-indians-will-die-waiting-for-us-green-card-says-study-4363584%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fover-4-lakh-indians-will-die-waiting-for-us-green-card-says-study-4363584%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suspect%20indicted%20on%20attempted%20murder%20charge%20in%20explosives%20attack%20on%20Japan's%20Kishida%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693971609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103414692%2Cimgsize-37114.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsuspect-indicted-on-attempted-murder-charge-in-explosiv