r%20the%20developing%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20not%20attend%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20this%20week%20and%20the%20delegation%20will%20be%20led%20by%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%2C%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20announced%20on%20Monday%20as%20it%20expressed%20Beijing's%20readiness%20to%20work%20with%20all%20parties%20to%20make%20the%20high-profile%20meeting%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20Premier%20of%20the%20State%20Council%20Li%20will%20attend%20the%2018th%20G20%20Summit%20to%20be%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20India%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%2C%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20Spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said%20in%20a%20brief%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20hosting%20the%20annual%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20September%209%20and%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20G-20%20Summit%2C%20Mr%20Sullivan%20said%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20will%20be%20clear%20that%20the%20United%20States%20expects%20real%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20will%20be%20clear%20that%20we%20need%20all%20G20%20members%20to%20be%20constructive%20and%20at%20the%20table%2C%20with%20no%20exceptions.%20We'll%20also%20be%20making%20progress%20on%20other%20key%20priorities%2C%20from%20climate%20to%20health%20to%20digital%20technology%2C%20including%20commitments%2C%20with%20respect%20to%20a%20more%20inclusive%20digital%20transformation%20and%20a%20responsible%20path%20and%20approach%20to%20AI%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20addition%2C%20we'll%20spotlight%20the%20progress%20that%20we've%20been%20making%20on%20the%20Partnership%20for%20Global%20Infrastructure%20Investment%2C%20or%20what%20we%20call%20PGI.%20We'll%20have%20some%20announcements%20that%20we're%20excited%20about.%20Now%2C%20we%20know%20that%20there%20will%20be%20continued%20focus%20on%20how%20the%20G20%20deals%20with%20Russia's%20illegal%20and%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sullivan%20said%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20Russia's%20illegal%20war%20has%20devastated%20social%20and%20economic%20consequences%2C%20and%20the%20poorest%20countries%20on%20the%20planet%20are%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20has%20done%20before%2C%20President%20Biden%20will%20call%20for%20a%20just%20and%20durable%20peace%20founded%20in%20respect%20for%20international%20law%2C%20principles%20of%20the%20UN%20Charter%2C%20the%20precepts%20of%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sullivan%20said%20Biden%20will%20continue%20to%20emphasise%20that%20the%20United%20States%20will%20support%20Ukraine%20for%20as%20long%20as%20it%20takes%20to%20redeem%20these%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20but%20not%20least%2C%20and%20this%20is%20important%2C%20you'll%20see%20that%20the%20United%20States%20will%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20we%20remain%20committed%20to%20the%20G20%2C%20as%20a%20critical%20forum%20for%20all%20of%20the%20major%20economies%20of%20the%20world%20to%20come%20together%20for%20global%20problem-solving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20international%20economy%20is%20suffering%20from%20historic%20and%20overlapping%20shocks%2C%20it%20is%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20to%20have%20a%20working%20forum%20with%20the%20world's%20largest%20economies%20to%20deliver%20meaningful%20outcomes%2C%20Mr%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20a%20sign%20of%20that%20commitment%2C%20the%20United%20States%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20hosting%20the%20G20%20in%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20eminent%20American%20expert%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Chian's%20decision%20to%20skip%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20point