But%20for%20youngsters%2C%20I%20think%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20new%20experience%20and%20they%20will%20be%20okay%20with%20that.%20But%20yes%2C%20a%20transition%20from%20India%20to%20Bharat%20is%20going%20to%20be%20really%20challenging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Indian%20Olympic%20Association%C2%A0(IOA)%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20unveiled%20the%20much-anticipated%20official%20ceremonial%20dress%20and%20playing%20kit%20for%20the%20Indian%20contingent%20that%20will%20compete%20at%20the%20forthcoming%202022%C2%A0Asian%20Games%C2%A0scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20China%20from%20September%2023%20to%20October%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIOA%20also%20conducted%20a%20glittering%20send-off%20ceremony%20which%20was%20graced%20by%20the%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20and%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20Anurag%20Thakur%2C%20IOA%C2%A0President%20and%20legendary%20sprinter%C2%A0PT%20Usha%C2%A0along%20with%20other%20senior%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingent%20was%20represented%20by%20Indian%20hockey%20goalkeepers%C2%A0PR%20Sreejesh%C2%A0(men)%2C%C2%A0Savita%20Punia%C2%A0(women)%2C%20shooting%20sensation%20Manu%20Bhaker%20and%202018%C2%A0Asian%20Games%C2%A0shot%20put%20gold%20medallist%20Tajinderpal%20Singh%20Toor%20among%20sportspersons%20from%20many%20other%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2033%20members%2C%20rowing%20has%20the%20largest%20unit%20after%20athletics%20going%20to%20Hangzhou%20to%20stake%20claim%20at%20the%20medal.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%2015-member%20Esports%20team%20will%20also%20be%20at%20the%C2%A0Asian%20Games%C2%A0as%20the%20event%20makes%20its%20official%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingent%20clinched%2070%20medals%2C%20including%2016%20gold%2C%20in%20the%20last%20edition%20of%20the%C2%A0Asian%20Games%20held%20in%202018%2C%20its%20highest%20medal%20count%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20