icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbrazils-lula-legalizes-more-indigenous-reservations-in-amazon%2Farticleshow%2F103406288.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbrazils-lula-legalizes-more-indigenous-reservations-in-amazon%2Famp_articleshow%2F103406288.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbrazils-lula-legalizes-more-indigenous-reservations-in-amazon%2Famp_articleshow%2F103406288.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20Mohammad%20Akbar%20Lone%2C%20the%20Politician%20Asked%20by%20the%20SC%20to%20File%20an%20Allegiance%20Affidavit%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F15163540%2Flone.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Senior%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Mohammad%20Akbar%20Lone%2C%20whose%20credentials%20have%20come%20under%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20scanner%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20leaders%20from%20the%20old%20guard%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20mainstream%20political%20spectrum%20to%20have%20upheld%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20in%20the%20troubled%20region%20despite%20grave%20risks%20and%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hot-headed%20politician%20with%20foot-in-mouth%20syndrome%2C%20Lone%20was%20asked%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20bench%20that%20is%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20Article%20370%20petitions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-akbar-lone-centre-pakistan-zindabad-slogans-8923385%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20file%20an%20affidavit%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Caccepting%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20%5BJammu%20and%20Kashmir%5D%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India%20and%20he%20abides%20by%20and%20owes%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20%5Bof%20India%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20direction%20came%20after%20solicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20while%20referring%20to%20%E2%80%98Pakistan%20%3Cem%3Ezindabad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20slogans%20Lone%20raised%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%20in%202018%2C%20told%20the%20constitution%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20north%20Kashmir%2C%20who%20is%20the%20lead%20petitioner%20in%20Article%20370%20case%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FLU%2F05092023_133725.pdf%5C%22%3Esupports%20separatist%20elements%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20close%20to%20the%20National%20Conference%20leader%20said%20that%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20process%20of%20following%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20direction%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20preparing%20the%20document%20sought%20by%20the%20court.%20The%20affidavit%20that%20Lone%20%3Cem%3Esaheb%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20submitted%20before%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20for%20contesting%20%5Bthe%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%5D%20from%20north%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20attached%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFrom%20landowner%20to%20politician%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20family%20of%20landlords%20who%20cultivated%20rice%2C%20apples%20and%20linseed%20in%20Bandipora%E2%80%99s%20Naidkhai%20village%2C%20Lone%20climbed%20the%20political%20ladder%20in%20the%20turbulence-ridden%20landscape%20of%20Kashmir%20with%20both%20perseverance%20and%20political%20gimmickry%2C%20often%20deploying%20foul%20diction%20and%20repulsive%20body%20signs%20to%20criticise%20his%20opponents%20in%20full%20public%20glare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumnus%20of%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%E2%80%99s%20law%20department%2C%20the%20senior%20National%20Conference%20leader%20has%20been%20active%20in%20politics%20for%20nearly%20five%20decades%2C%20riding%20the%20tides%20of%20both%20the%20conflict%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20strong%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20member%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20Lone%20remains%20undefeated%20from%20his%20home%20turf%20of%20Sonawari%20constituency%20in%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Bandipora%20district%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F11144557%2FJayaprakash_Narayan_2001_stamp_of_India-300x142.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F11144557%2FJayaprakash_Narayan_2001_stamp_of_India-300x142.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F11144557%2FJayaprakash_Narayan_2001_stamp_of_India.jpg%20946w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-404457%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22142%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Janata%20Party%20was%20formed%20by%20anti-corruption%20crusader%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20(and%20others)%20in%201977.%20Photo%3A%20Government%20of%20India%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELone%20fought%20his%20first%20assembly%20election%20in%201977%20on%20a%20Janata%20Party%20ticket%20when%20he%20was%20denied%20a%20mandate%20by%20the%20Sheikh%20Abdullah-led%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Janata%20Party%20came%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%20the%201977%20general%20elections%2C%20Lone%20lost%20his%20first%20bid%20to%20enter%20the%20power%20corridors%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20In%20the%20next%20year%2C%20though%2C%20he%20became%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Conference%2C%20a%20mainstream-turned-separatist-%3Cwbr%3Eturned-mainstream%20political%20party%20now%20headed%20by%20Sajad%20Lone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-time%20lawmaker%20from%20Sonawari%2C%20Lone%20fought%20the%201983%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%20elections%20on%20a%20People%E2%80%99s%20Conference%20ticket%2C%20but%20lost%20the%20fight%20to%20Ghulam%20Rasool%20Bahar%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20a%20party%20Lone%20would%20join%20four%20years%20later%20in%201987%20and%20continues%20to%20serve%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EStanding%20against%20Ikhwan%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20conflict%20erupted%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20Lone%20took%20on%20the%20Ikhwan-ul-Muslimoon%2C%20a%20state-backed%20counter-insurgency%20militia%20headed%20by%20Mohammad%20Yusuf%20Parray%20alias%20Kuka%20Parray%2C%20which%20has%20been%20blamed%20for%20some%20of%20the%20most%20bone-chilling%20human%20rights%20abuses%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20the%20abduction%2C%20murder%20and%20rape%20of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELone%E2%80%99s%20vocal%20stand%20against%20the%20abuses%20by%20Parray%20and%20his%20men%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Kashmir%20had%20fallen%20into%20anarchy%20won%20him%20both%20admirers%20and%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20Kashmiri%20journalist%2C%20Lone%20was%20targeted%20allegedly%20by%20Ikhwanis%20as%20well%20as%20militants%20multiple%20times%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20with%20even%20a%20reward%20being%20put%20on%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuka%20Parray%20and%20other%20Ikhwanis%20accused%20him%20of%20working%20for%20the%20agencies%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20while%20the%20militants%20labelled%20him%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstooge%E2%80%9D%20of%20India%20for%20joining%20the%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20single%20day%2C%20several%20of%20his%20workers%20were%20killed%20in%20Saderkoot%20by%20a%20notorious%20Ikhwani%20of%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20journalist%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Ikhwan%20presiding%20over%20a%20reign%20of%20terror%20across%20Kashmir%2C%20Lone%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20continued%20to%20surge.%20In%20the%201996%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20fielded%20him%20from%20Sonawari%20constituency%20against%20Parray%2C%20in%20what%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20watched%20electoral%20battles%20in%20the%20post-1989%20history%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELone%2C%20a%20former%20state%20cabinet%20minister%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%20speaker%2C%20was%20handed%20a%20massive%20defeat%20by%20Parrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frashid-billa-kashmir-ikhwan%5C%22%3EThe%20Life%20and%20Death%20of%20a%20Pro-Government%20Militant%20in%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAn%20unbroken%20stint%20in%20power%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20election%20of%202002%2C%20Lone%20went%20on%20to%20defeat%20Parray%2C%20which%20also%20marked%20Ikhwan%E2%80%99s%20end%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Lone%20has%20remained%20unbeaten%20in%20two%20consecutive%20assembly%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%93%20in%202008%20and%202014%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Sonawari%2C%20a%20seat%20which%20is%20now%20eyed%20by%20his%20elder%20son%2C%20Hilal%20Akbar%20Lone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20political%20career%20has%20been%20marred%20by%20controversies%20of%20his%20own%20making.%20Opponents%20have%20termed%20him%20%E2%80%9Cmentally%20unfit%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20his%20vituperative%20outbursts%2C%20while%20Omar%20Abdullah%20called%20him%20a%20person%20who%20%E2%80%9Coften%20raises%20my%20blood%20pressure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELone%20once%20accused%20the%20Army%20of%20attempting%20to%20revive%20the%20Ikhwan%20in%20Kashmir%20after%20stones%20were%20hurled%20at%20his%20cavalcade%20in%20north%20Kashmir.%20His%20remarks%20earned%20him%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20party%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20speaker%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%2C%20Lone%20hurled%20from%20his%20podium%20nasty%20abuses%20at%20Molvi%20Iftikhar%20Ansari%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Conference%20and%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20minister%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia%2Fabuses-fans-fly-in-j-k-house%2Fstory-ontT1MMvw1tY57x7vpWpOI.html%5C%22%3Ewho%20in%20turn%20unsuccessfully%20attempted%20to%20fling%20a%20standing%20fan%20at%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20episode%20(in%202011)%20marked%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20points%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20history%2C%20and%20Lone%20later%20regretted%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELone%20has%20three%20sons%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20%E2%80%93%20Hilal%20Akbar%20Lone%20and%20Bilal%20Akbar%20Lone%20%E2%80%93%20are%20also%20active%20in%20politics.%20Hilal%20was%20among%20the%20dozens%20of%20political%20detainees%20who%20were%20lodged%20at%20a%20hotel-turned-jail%20in%20Srinagar%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fhilal-lone-latest-jammu-kashmir-politician-to-be-booked-under-psa%2F362752%2F%5C%22%3EHe%20was%20subsequently%20booked%20under%20the%20draconian%20Public%20Safety%20Act.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20also%20booked%20Hilal%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fakbar-lones-son-booked-under-uapa-for-poll-speech%2Farticle33849938.ece%5C%22%3EUnlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20he%20made%20a%20controversial%20speech%20in%202020%20as%20part%20of%20the%20district%20development%20council%20poll%20campaign%20in%20the%20Sonawari%20assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-action-against-nc-mla-lone-for-raising-pr