ent%20and%20development%20of%20China-India%20relations%20is%20in%20the%20common%20interest%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20the%20two%20peoples%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20India%20to%20promote%20greater%20development%20of%20China-India%20relations%2C%E2%80%9D%20noted%20Mao.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20China%20have%20largely%20remained%20frozen%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20border%20stand-off%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20clash%20that%20killed%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20four%20Chinese%20soldiers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20leading%20to%20disengagement%20in%20around%20four%20to%20five%20points.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fexplained-what-are-the-friction-points-on-the-lac%2Farticle66928561.ece%5C%22%3Etwo%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20which%20both%20sides%20remain%20eyeball-to-eyeball%20in%20the%20high%20Himalayas%20at%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20not%20held%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20since%202019.%20There%20have%20been%20ministerial%20meetings%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20various%20multilateral%20events%2C%20but%20India%20has%20indicated%20that%20they%20were%20limited%20to%20discussing%20the%20border%20stand-off.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond%20to%20Xi%E2%80%99s%20absence%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F09%2F04%2Fdel70-g20-jaishankar.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%