0kilometres%20of%20area%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%2028%2C55%2C794%20people%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censusindia2011.com%2Fmanipur-population.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DManipur%2520Population%2520%252D%2520Census%2520India%25202011%26amp%3Btext%3DAs%2520per%2520the%2520Census%2520India%2Cis%252013.14%2525%2520of%2520total%2520population.%5C%22%3E2011%20Census.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20Regional%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20a%20state%20hospital%2C%20seven%20district%20hospitals%2C%20one%20sub-district%20hospital%2C%2016%20community%20health%20centres%2C%2080%20primary%20health%20centres%2C%20413%20sub-centres%20and%2033%20private%20hospitals%2Fclinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20also%20has%20a%20fairly%20decent%20sex%20ratio%20of%20987%20girls%20born%20for%20every%201%2C000%20boys.%20The%20ratio%20declines%20to%20957%20girls%20for%20every%201%2C000%20boys%20for%20ages%20below%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202023-24%20budget%2C%20the%20state%20increased%20its%20allocation%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbudgets%2Fstates%2Fmanipur-budget-analysis-2023-24%5C%22%3E10%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20to%20ramp%20up%20health%20facilities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20understand%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20culture%20and%20history%20to%20get%20a%20complete%20picture%20of%20their%20healthcare%20system%20and%20the%20various%20stakeholders%20involved%20in%20its%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvolution%20of%20healthcare%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20A%20comparison%20between%20NFHS-4%20and%20NFHS-5%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%20has%20gone%20through%20several%20phases%20of%20development.%20In%20the%20early%20years%2C%20healthcare%20was%20primarily%20limited%20to%20traditional%20practices%20and%20local%20remedies.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20modern%20medicine%2C%20the%20state%20saw%20the%20establishment%20of%20government-run%20healthcare%20centres%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20of%20immunisation%20programmes%20and%20family%20planning%20initiatives%20further%20enhanced%20healthcare%20services%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Manipur%20still%20faces%20plenty%20of%20healthcare%20issues%20which%20add%20to%20the%20socio-economic%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20its%20residents.%20The%20poor%20condition%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20affects%20some%20communities%20more%20than%20the%20others.%20These%20include%20women%2C%20children%2C%20senior%20citizens%2C%20and%20people%20with%20different%20ailments.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20paramount%20to%20look%20at%20the%20statistics%20when%20analysing%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20in%20any%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20expenditure%20on%20healthcare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS)-4%2C%202015-16%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20per%20capita%20public%20health%20expenditure%20stands%20at%20Rs%201%2C364.%20This%20is%20almost%20three%20times%20that%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20double%20the%20expenditure%20of%20Punjab%20and%20the%20national%20average%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20such%20a%20high%20expenditure%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20households%20with%20any%20usual%20member%20covered%20by%20a%20health%20scheme%20or%20health%20insurance%20is%20only%203.6%25%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20lower%20than%20the%20national%20average%20of%2028.7%25.%20The%20coverage%20is%20even%20more%20limited%20in%20the%20hilly%20districts%2C%20with%20Senapati%2C%20Ukhrul%2C%20and%20Chandel%20having%20coverage%20rates%20of%20only%200.6%25%2C%201%25%2C%20and%201.1%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20indicates%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20population%20pays%20for%20medical%20expenses%20out%20of%20their%20own%20pockets%2C%20leading%20to%20financial%20burden%20and%20challenges%20in%20accessing%20quality%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05172527%2Fimage-1279.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05172527%2Fimage-1279.png%20910w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05172527%2Fimage-1279-300x139.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22423%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Team%20InfoSphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05173014%2Fimage-1281.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22917%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05173014%2Fimage-1281.png%20917w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05173014%2Fimage-1281-300x127.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671569%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22387%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Team%20InfoSphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05173114%2Fimage-1282.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22927%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05173114%2Fimage-1282.png%20927w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05173114%2Fimage-1282-300x146.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671570%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Infosphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20indicators%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NFHS-4%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20(IMR)%20stands%20at%2022%2C%20which%20is%20lower%20than%20the%20national%20average%20of%2041.%20The%20figures%20indicate%20a%20better%20infant%20health%20outcome%20in%20the%20state%20compared%20to%20the%20country%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Manipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fhiv-prevalence-rate-among-adults-highest-in-manipur-study%2Fstory-8qpmdnceFybIqJxXTr5Z5N.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20the%20highest%20prevalence%20of%20HIV%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20adult%20population%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20a%20rate%20of%201.15%25.%20This%20is%20four%20times%20the%20all-India%20average%20and%20indicates%20a%20significant%20public%20health%20challenge%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20over%20half%20of%20the%20deliveries%20in%20private%20health%20facilities%20in%20urban%20Manipur%20are%20performed%20by%20a%20caesarean%20section%2C%20while%20the%20percentage%20is%20lower%20(30%25)%20in%20public%20health%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-healthcare-education-government-reel-under-violence%5C%22%3EMedicine%20Shortages%2C%20Uncertain%20Educational%20Futures%3A%20Manipur%20Is%20Reeling%20Under%20Many%20Impacts%20of%20Violence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20manpower%20and%20infrastructure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NFHS-4%20and%20District%20Level%20Household%20and%20Facility%20Survey%204%2C%20Manipur%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20nurses%20per%20capita%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20after%20Kerala.%20This%20indicates%20a%20relatively%20better%20availability%20of%20nursing%20staff%20for%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05174321%2Fimage-1283.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05174321%2Fimage-1283.png%20771w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05174321%2Fimage-1283-300x158.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671571%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22475%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Infosphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsights%20from%20NFHS-5%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%20surveyed%20households%20in%20the%20NFHS%2C%20around%2072%25%20had%20access%20to%20basic%20drinking%20water%20services.%20However%2C%20only%2020.5%25%20of%20the%20households%20had%20water%20piped%20into%20their%20dwelling%2C%20yard%20or%20plot.%20Around%2062%25%20of%20households%20in%20Manipur%20had%20basic%20sanitation%20service%20(improved%20facilities%20not%20shared%20among%20households)%20while%2032%25%20had%20limited%20sanitation%20services%20(improved%20sanitation%20facilities%20shared%20by%20two%20or%20more%20households).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20few%20as%200.5%25%20of%20households%20in%20the%20state%20had%20no%20sanitation%20facility%20and%20used%20open%20spaces%20or%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NFHS-5%2C%20the%20total%20fertility%20rate%20(TFR)%20in%20Manipur%20was%202.17%20children%20per%20woman%3B%20it%20was%202.38%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%201.84%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20was%20a%20decline%20from%20the%20TFR%20of%202.61%20children%20per%20woman%20recorded%20in%20NFHS-4.%20Knowledge%20of%20contraceptive%20methods%20was%20almost%20universal%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20married%20women%2C%20the%20use%20of%20contraception%20rose%20steeply%20from%2023.6%25%20in%20NFHS-4%20to%2061.3%25%20in%20NFHS-5.%20However%2C%20only%2018.2%25%20of%20the%20women%20used%20modern%20methods%20of%20contraception%20such%20as%20sterilisation%2C%20pill%2C%20intrauterine%20devices%2C%20injectables%2C%20or%20condoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20NHFS-5%2C%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20(IMR)%20was%2025%2C%20(meaning%2025%20deaths%20before%20the%20age%20of%20one%20per%201%2C000%20live%20births).%20In%20NFHS-4%2C%20IMR%20was%2021.7.%20The%20under-five%20mortality%20rate%20during%20the%20period%20remained%20nearly%20the%20same%20at%20around%2030%2C%20(meaning%2030%20deaths%20before%20the%20age%20of%20five%20per%201%2C000%20live%20births).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20teams%20have%20been%20constituted%20in%20each%20of%20the%20affected%20districts%20in%20Manipur%20to%20provide%20overall%20healthcare%20services%20to%20the%20victims%20at%20the%20designated%20relief%20camps.%20Regular%20health%20check-ups%20are%20conducted%20at%20all%20the%20designated%20relief%20camps%20across%20the%20state%2C%20and%20those%20who%20are%20seriously%20ill%20are%20promptly%20transferred%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospitals%20by%20ambulance%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20healthcare%20services%20for%20women%20and%20children%2C%20including%20lactating%20mothers%20and%20infants%2C%20are%20provided%20under%20the%20maternal%20health%20and%20child%20health%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05175720%2Fimage-1284.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22954%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05175720%2Fimage-1284.png%20954w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05175720%2Fimage-1284-300x193.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671573%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Infosphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%2068.8%25%20of%20children%20in%20Manipur%2C%20aged%2012-23%20months%2C%20received%20all%20basic%20vaccinations%20against%20tuberculosis%2C%20diphtheria%2C%20pertussis%2C%20tetanus%2C%20polio%2C%20and%20measles.%20Only%20around%202.8%25%20of%20children%20(aged%2012-23%20months)%20in%20the%20state%20had%20not%20received%20any%20vaccinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2042%25%20of%20children%20(aged%20between%20six%20and%2059%20months)%20in%20the%20state%20suffered%20from%20anaemia%20%E2%80%93%20a%20substantial%20increase%20from%20the%20NFHS-4%20estimate%20of%2022.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%2063.8%25%20of%20women%20used%20cloth%2C%2080.9%25%20used%20sanitary%20napkins%2C%203.9%25%20used%20locally%20prepared%20napkins%2C%200.7%25%20used%20menstrual%20cups%20and%200.1%25%20used%20tampons.%20Thirty-seven%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20(aged%20between%2018%20to%2049%20years)%20in%20the%20state%20reported%20having%20experienced%20either%20physical%20or%20sexual%20violence%20and%204%25%20reported%20having%20experienced%20both.%20However%2C%20only%203%25%20of%20women%20who%20had%20experienced%20such%20violence%20sought%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20put%20some%20of%20these%20numbers%20in%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20district-level%20insight%20from%20the%20NFHS%20surveys%20and%20other%20sources%20may%20help%20provide%20greater%20depth%20to%20our%20team%E2%80%99s%20analysis%2C%20however%2C%20access%20to%20these%20figures%20and%20granular%20details%20remains%20a%20challenge.%20Our%20team%20also%20faced%20these%20challenges.%20If%20we%20could%20overcome%20these%20challenges%2C%20through%20better%20(high%20frequency)%20data%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20helpful%20for%20both%20context%20and%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssessing%20the%20socio-political%20and%20economic%20situation%20in%20a%20conflict-affected%20area%20leads%20to%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20demographic%E2%80%99s%20public%20health%20scenario%2C%20too.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Manipur%2C%20too%2C%20many%20issues%20highlighted%20in%20this%20piece%20have%20been%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20children%20and%20elderly%2C%20who%20have%20all%20been%20badly%20affected%20by%20the%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20this%20series%20shall%20reflect%20more%20on%20the%20role%20of%20other%20factors%20responsible%20for%20the%20healthcare%20implications%20of%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eis%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAmisha%20Singh%2C%20Aditi%20Desai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shalaka%20Adhikari%2C%20Samragnee%20Chakraborty%2C%20Shilpa%20Santhosh%20and%20Vasudevan%20%3Cem%3Eare%20Research%20Analysts%20with%20CNES%20and%20members%20of%20the%20InfoSphere%20Team.%20The%20authors%20thank%20Dr%20Samrat%20Sinha%20for%20his%20constant%20guidance%2C%20help%20and%20support.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20previous%20field%20studies%20from%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20work%20on%20Manipur%20can%20be%20accessed%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fauthor%2F1779734%2Fsamrat-sinha%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frelief-manipur-trucks%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-multi-faceted-economic-ramifications-of-manipurs-ethnic-conflict%23read-more%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-sexual-violence-bjp-apathy-patriarchy%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693920656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12081122%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.08.47-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fassessing-manipurs-healthcare-challenges-amidst-the-ongoing-crisis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20crucial%20to%20understand%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20culture%20and%20history%20to%20get%20a%20complete%20picture%20of%20their%20healthcare%20system%20and%20the%20various%20stakeholders%20involved%20in%20its%20development.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fassessing-manipurs-healthcare-challenges-amidst-the-ongoing-crisis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Friends%20Are%20Taking%20ICUs%20to%20Rural%20India%20With%20a%20Simple%20Kit%20%26amp%3B%20An%20Innovative%20Idea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20a%20story%20of%20a%20pregnant%20Munni%20Devi%20%E2%80%94%20a%20resident%20of%20Dhongri%20village%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Hazaribag%20district%20%E2%80%94%20who%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20nightmarish%20ordeal%20once%20her%20labour%20pains%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeteriorating%20road%20connectivity%20in%20the%20area%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328138%2Fmadurai-dr-swaminathan-doctor-on-wheels-takes-affordable-healthcare-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeant%20no%20ambulance%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20make%20it%20in%20time%20to%20Munni%E2%80%99s%20home.%20Her%20husband%20Surendra%20Kishku%20along%20with%20a%20few%20family%20members%20knew%20help%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20coming.%20A%20picture%20in%20the%20paper%20the%20next%20day%20showed%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20supporting%20the%2022-year-old%20woman%20as%20they%20undertook%20the%207%20km%20walk%20to%20Fufundih%20village%20where%20the%20ambulance%20was%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20report%20filed%20in%20April%202023%20by%20%3Cem%3EAP%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20highlighted%20the%20loopholes%20in%20the%20medical%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20country%20through%20the%20story%20of%2019-year-old%20Poonam%20Gond.%20The%20Chhatisgarh%20native%20battles%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20%E2%80%94%20a%20genetic%20blood%20disorder%20that%20necessitates%20frequent%20blood%20transfusions.%20But%20as%20the%20report%20cited%2C%20%E2%80%9Cone%20doctor%20for%20every%2016%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%9D%20meant%20Gond%20was%20not%20on%20the%20priority%20list.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20list%20was%20endless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20instances%20underline%20the%20domino%20effect%20that%20understaffed%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326524%2Ffood-for-patiets-of-diabetes-cancer-pcos-home-delivery-hypothalamus-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunder-resourced%20rural%20hospitals%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20have%20on%20patient%20care.%20But%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccitizen-led%20initiative%E2%80%9D%20spearheaded%20by%20three%20friends%20is%20attempting%20to%20change%20this%20grim%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%20the%20nation%2C%20Mission%20ICU%20was%20conceived%20by%20Dr%20Ashwin%20Naik