3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20required%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fif-need-be-i-will-behead-udhayanidhi-stalin-myself-ayodhya-seer-paramhans-acharya-reacts-to-sanatan-dharma-remark-541541%5C%22%3EI%20myself%20will%20behead%20MK%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20and%20I%20will%20also%20increase%20the%20bounty%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20if%20that%20is%20not%20enough%20for%20beheading%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Das%20was%20quoted%20by%20ANI%20as%20saying%20on%20Tuesday%20(September%205).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHead%20priest%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Tapasvi%20Chhawni%20temple%2C%20Das%20on%20Monday%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fayodhya-seer-announces-10cr-bounty-on-head-of-stalins-son%2Farticleshow%2F103373244.cms%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20cash%20reward%20for%20anyone%20who%20%E2%80%9Cbeheads%E2%80%9D%20Stalin%20over%20his%20%E2%80%98anti-sanatana%20Dharma%E2%80%99%20remark%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(TOI)%20reported.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20how%20he%E2%80%99ll%20pay%20the%20hefty%20sum%2C%20Das%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20owner%20of%20Rs%20500%20crore%20and%20paying%20Rs%2010%20crore%20is%20nothing%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20May%20End%20Up%20Tying%20Itself%20In%20Knots%20By%20Attacking%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20him%20to%20first%20read%20the%20history%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20and%20then%20comment%20against%20it.%20He%20should%20apologise%20for%20whatever%20he%20has%20said%20against%20our%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20and%20if%20he%20does%20not%20apologise%2C%20no%20matter%20if%20he%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20will%20get%20the%20punishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Das%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStalin%2C%20while%20attending%20an%20event%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatana%20Ozhippu%20Maanaadu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20%5B%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conclave%E2%80%99%5D%20organised%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Progressive%20Writers%20and%20Artists%20Association%20to%20critique%20the%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20congratulate%20the%20organisers%20for%20calling%20the%20conference%20as%20%E2%80%98eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%98opposing%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20certain%20things%20which%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20and%20we%20cannot%20merely%20oppose.%20Mosquitoes%2C%20dengue%2C%20corona%20and%20malaria%20are%20things%20which%20we%20cannot%20oppose%2C%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20them.%20Sanatanam%20is%20also%20like%20this.%20Eradication%20and%20not%20opposing%20sanatanam%20has%20to%20be%20our%20first%20task.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20sparked%20a%20controversy%20after%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20IT%20cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20interpreted%20the%20remarks%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccall%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20genocide%E2%80%9D%20of%20sanatanis%2C%20who%20he%20claimed%20comprise%20%E2%80%9C80%25%20%5Bof%20the%5D%20population%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693918249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04213611%2FUdhayanidhi.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-behead-udhayanidi-stalin-myself-if-required-paramhans-das-on-sanatana-dharma-remarks%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stalin%20was%20attending%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Progressive%20Writers%20and%20Artists%20Association%20to%20critique%20the%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20when%20he%20made%20the%20remark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-behead-udhayanidi-stalin-myself-if-required-paramhans-das-on-sanatana-dharma-remarks%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Understanding%20GDP%20Growth%20Through%20Discrepancies%20and%20Why%20the%20Major%20Push%20Is%20Not%20Visible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F05211159%2FGDP-PTI.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quarterly%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20numbers%20for%20the%20first%20quarter%20(Q1)%20of%202023-24%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgdp-grew-by-7-8-pc-yoy-this-q1-nso-says%5C%22%3Ewere%20released%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20August%2031.%20They%20show%20real%20growth%20(less%20inflation)%20of%207.8%25%20for%20both%20GDP%20and%20gross%20value%20added%20(GVA)%20over%20Q1%20of%202022-23%20(previous%20year).%20This%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20estimates%20given%20earlier%20by%20analysts%2C%20RBI%20and%20international%20agencies.%20It%20is%20much%20higher%20than%20what%20has%20been%20achieved%20by%20other%20major%20economies%20of%20the%20world%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20China%2C%20the%20US%20or%20Germany.%20It%20buttresses%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20managing%20the%20economy%20well%20and%20being%20a%20world%20leader%20(Vishwaguru).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20claims%20depend%20on%20how%20accurate%20the%20data%20is.%20Of%20late%2C%20various%20top%20functionaries%20have%20questioned%20the%20credibility%20of%20official%20data.%20It%20has%20been%20pointed%20out%20that%20sample%20surveys%20that%20underlie%20a%20lot%20of%20macro%20data%20are%20now%20dated%20since%20there%20has%20been%20no%20Census%20after%202011%20while%20there%20have%20been%20structural%20changes%20in%20the%20economy%20since%20that%20time.%20Further%2C%20this%20author%20has%20repeatedly%20pointed%20out%20that%20since%202017%2C%20the%20non-agricultural%20unorganised%20sector%20is%20not%20independently%20measured%20and%20is%20replaced%20by%20the%20organised%20sector.%20So%2C%20a%20declining%20sector%20replaced%20by%20the%20growing%20organised%20sector%20results%20in%20over-estimation%20of%20the%20GDP%20and%20other%20macro%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%20let%20us%20leave%20these%20errors%20out%20of%20the%20discussion%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20official%20figures%20released%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation%20(MOSPI).%20What%20do%20they%20show%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComparative%20growth%20rates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20high%20growth%20rate%20in%20Q1%20is%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20steep%20fall%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findia-economy-gdp-q1-decline-coronavirus-lockdown%5C%22%3E23.9%25%20in%20GDP%20in%20Q1%20of%202020-21%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20decline%20in%20India%20was%20the%20sharpest%20among%20the%20major%20world%20economies.%20None%20of%20the%20other%20countries%20saw%20the%20mass%20migration%20of%20people%20from%20cities%20to%20the%20villages%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20India.%20A%20recovery%20will%20show%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20GDP%20due%20to%20the%20low%20base.%20This%20has%20been%20playing%20out%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20Growth%20rates%20in%20Q1%20have%20been%2021.6%25%20in%202021-22%20and%2013.1%25%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20better%20to%20compare%20the%20Q1%202023-24%20numbers%20with%20the%20pre-pandemic%20year%20of%202019-20.%20So%2C%20the%20average%20growth%20in%20GVA%20turns%20out%20to%20be%203.5%25%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20This%20was%20also%20the%20growth%20rate%20pre-pandemic.%20So%2C%20the%20trend%20of%20low%20growth%20seems%20to%20be%20persisting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrivers%20of%20growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20look%20at%20the%20expenditure%20components%20of%20GDP%2C%20presented%20in%20the%20tables%20released%2C%20show%20that%20most%20components%20have%20declined%20as%20a%20share%20of%20GDP.%20Namely%2C%20private%20final%20consumption%2C%20government%20final%20consumption%2C%20valuables%20and%20exports.%20Imports%20have%20risen%20marginally%20while%20Gross%20Fixed%20Capital%20Formation%20(GFCF)%20and%20Change%20in%20Stocks%20(CIS)%20have%20remained%20unchanged.%20How%20can%20most%20of%20the%20shares%20have%20fallen%20unless%20some%20share%20has%20risen%3F%20Indeed%2C%20discrepancies%20as%20a%20share%20of%20GDP%20have%20seen%20a%20sharp%20increase%20from%20-3.4%25%20to%202.8%25%2C%20that%20is%206.2%25%20of%20the%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscrepancies%20represent%20the%20mismatch%20between%20the%20GDP%20numbers%20calculated%20by%20different%20methods.%20These%20are%20not%20a%20category%20of%20GDP%20expenditure.%20These%20are%20a%20sum%20of%20errors%20in%20various%20expenditure%20categories.%20These%20do%20not%20spur%20growth%20of%20the%20economy%20as%20the%20other%20expenditures%20signify.%20This%20needs%20to%20be%20further%20analysed%20when%20more%20data%20is%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20discrepancies%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20less%20than%201%25.%20But%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20in%20Indian%20data%2C%20these%20have%20been%20large.%20Like%2C%20now%20they%20have%20swung%20from%20a%20large%20negative%20number%20to%20a%20large%20positive%20one.%20Effectively%2C%20discrepancies%20are%20a%20pointer%20to%20errors%20in%20the%20GDP%20numbers%20due%20to%20methodological%20deficiencies%2C%20especially%20when%20there%20are%20shocks%20to%20the%20economy%2C%20such%20as%20demonetisation%2C%20structurally%20faulty%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20(GST)%20and%20the%20sudden%20lockdown.%20Such%20errors%20in%20the%20GDP%20numbers%20may%20suit%20the%20government%20since%20it%20would%20like%20to%20show%20a%20high%20growth%20rate%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drivers%20of%20growth%20in%20the%20economy%20are%20consumption%2C%20investment%2C%20government%20expenditures%20and%20net%20exports.%20Compared%20to%202022-23%2C%20their%20shares%20of%20the%20GDP%20have%20declined%20or%20stagnated.%20This%20should%20dampen%20growth.%20It%20would%20be%20better%20to%20compare%20the%20absolute%20numbers%20with%20the%20pre-pandemic%20figures%20since%20the%20previous%20two%20years%20were%20years%20of%20recovery%20from%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20also%20the%20ongoing%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20its%20global%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%202019-20%2C%20GDP%20has%20grown%2013.18%25.%20Private%20final%20consumption%20has%20risen%20by%2014.3%25%2C%20government%20final%20consumption%20by%203.8%25%20and%20fixed%20capital%20formation%20by%2013.6%25.%20So%2C%20none%20of%20these%20items%20are%20giving%20any%20boost%20to%20the%20economy.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20government%20is%20not%20at%20all%20pulling%20its%20weight%20in%20raising%20the%20growth%20rate.%20It%20should%20have%20been%20the%20capital%20formation%20that%20should%20have%20risen%20sharply%20to%20give%20the%20economy%20a%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contribution%20of%20Change%20in%20Stocks%20is%20-18.4%25%20and%20that%20of%20Valuables%20is%20-37.1%25.%20But%20these%20are%20small%20items%20compared%20to%20the%20big%20three%20items%20listed%20above.%20The%20other%20major%20item%20is%20the%20export%20surplus.%20This%20has%20also%20contributed%20negatively%20in%202023-24%20compared%20to%202019-20%20since%20imports%20have%20risen%20by%2025.6%25%2C%20while%20exports%20rose%20by%2019.4%25.%20So%2C%20the%20trade%20surplus%20has%20turned%20more%20negative%20than%20earlier%20and%20is%20a%20negative%20factor%20in%20boosting%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slow%20growth%20is%20due%20to%20a%20shortage%20of%20demand%20consequent%20to%20growing%20inequities%20which%20reduces%20demand%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20pyramid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20none%20of%20the%20growth%20drivers%20are%20giving%20a%20major%20boost%20to%20the%20economy%20compared%20to%202019-20.%20The%20current%20average%20growth%20rate%20of%203.5%25%20over%202019-20%2C%20the%20pre-pandemic%20year%2C%20is%20close%20to%20the%20pre-pandemic%20growth%20rate%20of%203.1%25%20in%20Q4%20of%202019-20.%20It%20had%20slowed%20down%20from%208.1%25%20growth%20in%20Q4%202017-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlow%20growth%20is%20due%20to%20the%20government%20policies%20which%20do%20not%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20boosting%20incomes%20and%20demand%20at%20the%20bottom.%20These%20policies%20are%20continuing%20with%20the%20government%20pushing%20for%20growth%20of%20the%20organised%20sector%20and%20capital%20intensive%20sectors%20resulting%20in%20high%20unemployment.%20Inflation%20is%20also%20pushing%20down%20purchasing%20power%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20pyramid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20good%20growth%20rate%20is%20largely%20a%20result%20of%20recovery%20from%20the%20massive%20decline%20in%20GDP%20in%20Q1%20of%202020-21%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArun%20Kumar%20is%20the%20author%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20Indian%20Economy%E2%80%99s%20Greatest%20Crisis%3A%20Impact%20of%20the%20Coronavirus%20and%20the%20Road%20Ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693917025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F05211159%2FGDP-PTI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funderstanding-gdp-growth-through-discrepancies-and-why-the-major-push-is-not-visible%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20high%20growth%20rate%20in%20Q1%20is%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20steep%20fall%20of%2023.9%25%20in%20GDP%20in%20Q1%20of%202020-21%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20A%20recovery%20will%20show%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20GDP%20due%20to%20the%20low%20base.%20This%20has%20been%20playing%20out%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funderstanding-gdp-growth-through-discrepancies-and-why-the-major-push-is-not-visible%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Patent%20Over%20Product%20or%20Process%3F%20The%20Story%20of%20an%20Ongoing%20Patent%20Tussle%20in%20the%20Delhi%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05164557%2FIntravenous-intravention.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPatents%20serve%20as%20gateways%20to%20ground-breaking%20innovations%20that%20profoundly%20impact%20societal%20welfare%2C%20from%20life-saving%20pharmaceuticals%20to%20revolutionary%20technological%20advancements.%20It%20is%20critical%20to%2C%20therefore%2C%20balance%20the%20interests%20of%20patentees%20in%20being%20duly%20incentivised%20for%20their%20innovation%20with%20the%20public%20interest%20in%20ensuring%20broad%20accessibility%20to%20their%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20unique%20institutional%20context%20in%20which%20the%20Patents%20Act%2C%201970%2C%20came%20into%20force%2C%20serves%20as%20the%20backdrop%20for%20this%20balancing.%20Being%20sensitive%20to%20the%20unique%20%E2%80%98facilitating%20circumstances%20and%20precipitating%20conditions%E2%80%99%20(this%20phrasing%20is%20taken%20from%20Laurence%20Helfer)%20that%20informed%20the%20formulation%20of%20modern%20Indian%20patent%20law%20can%20help%20us%20in%20arriving%20at%20concrete%20pathways%20for%20ensuring%20that%20the%20monopoly%20granted%20by%20patents%20does%20not%20impede%20the%20public%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayyangar%20Committee%20report%2C%20which%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20modern%20Indian%20patent%20law%2C%20boldly%20declared%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CPatent%20systems%20are%20not%20created%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20inventor%20but%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20national%20economy%E2%80%A6%20The%20precise%20provisions%20of%20the%20patent%20law%2C%20however%2C%20have%20to%20be%20designed%20with%20special%20reference%20to%20the%20economic%20conditions%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20state%20of%20its%20scientific%20and%20technological%20advance%2C%20its%20future%20needs%20and%20other%20relev%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eant%20factors%20and%20so%20as%20to%20minimise%20if%20not%20to%20eliminate%20the%20abuses%20to%20which%20a%20system%20of%20patent%20monopoly%20is%20capable%20of%20being%20put.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20a%20public-facing%20justification%20was%20the%20clear%20animating%20force%20that%20informed%20the%20determination%20of%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20patent%20protection%20should%20be%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20a%20legal%20dispute%20currently%20brewing%20in%20the%20courts%20of%20Delhi%20assumes%20significance.%20The%20clash%20between%20Vifor%20International%20Limited%20and%20MSN%20Laboratories%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20nuanced%20questions%20as%20to%20the%20scope%20and%20limits%20of%20a%20patent%20grant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20issue%20are%20patent%20rights%20over%20the%20drug%20ferric%20carboxymaltose%20(FCM)%20%E2%80%93%20an%20intravenous%20intervention%20for%20patients%20affected%20by%20iron%20deficiency%2Fanaemia%20when%20oral%20iron%20preparations%20are%20ineffective%20or%20cannot%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVifor%20claimed%20that%20during%20routine%20online%20surveillance%20around%20December%202020%2C%20it%20discovered%20that%20MSN%20was%20planning%20to%20launch%20a%20generic%20version%20of%20FCM%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20%E2%80%98Feinj%E2%80%99%2C%20resulting%20in%20its%20lawsuit%20against%20MSN%20to%20stop%20the%20sale%20of%20Feinj.%20A%20key%20point%20of%20contestation%20was%20whether%20Vifor%E2%80%99s%20monopoly%20over%20FCM%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20process%20that%20it%20had%20followed%20for%20making%20FCM%20or%20would%20also%20extend%20to%20any%20other%20process%20for%20manufacturing%20FCM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVifor%E2%80%99s%20submission%20was%20that%20all%20processes%20for%20manufacturing%20FCM%20were%20covered%20within%20the%20remit%20of%20its%20patent%20grant%20(making%20it%20a%20patent%20over%20the%20product%20per%20se)%2C%20while%20MSN%20argued%20that%20since%20it%20followed%20a%20different%20process%20for%20manufacturing%20FCM%2C%20Vifor%20could%20not%20stop%20it%20from%20doing%20so%20(making%20FCM%E2%80%99s%20patent%20a%20product%20by%20process%20patent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fhealth%2Ftrade-covid-19-vaccines-waiver%2F%5C%22%3EHow%20Trade%20Rules%20Affect%20Access%20to%20COVID-19%20Vaccines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20why%20the%20seemingly%20insignificant%20distinction%20between%20product%20patents%20per%20se%20versus%20product%20by%20process%20patents%20matters%2C%20let%20us%20consider%20a%20couple%20of%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssume%20that%20a%20pharmaceutical%20company%20develops%20a%20manufacturing%20process%20to%20produce%20a%20life-saving%20medication.%20Instead%20of%20patenting%20the%20medication%20itself%2C%20they%20patent%20the%20specific%20process%20used%20to%20create%20the%20medication.%20This%20allows%20the%20company%20to%20protect%20their%20innovative%20manufacturing%20method%20while%20enabling%20other%20companies%20to%20develop%20alternative%20processes%20to%20create%20the%20same%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20vein%2C%20assume%20that%20a%20company%20develops%20an%20innovative%20process%20to%20manufacture%20high-efficiency%20solar%20panels%20that%20generate%20more%20electricity%20than%20traditional%20panels.%20Instead%20of%20patenting%20the%20solar%20panels%20themselves%2C%20they%20patent%20the%20unique%20manufacturing%20process%20that%20enhances%20their%20performance.%20The%20patenting%20of%20the%20product%20through%20the%20given%20process%20rather%20than%20the%20product%20per%20se%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20other%20researchers%20and%20manufacturers%20to%20explore%20similar%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20product%20patents%20are%20per%20se%20bad%20%E2%80%93%20an%20issue%20which%20in%20any%20event%20is%20academic%2C%20given%20that%20the%20Patents%20Act%2C%20since%20its%20amendment%20in%202005%2C%20expressly%20allows%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20product%20patents%20on%20pharmaceuticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20we%20make%20is%20different.%20When%20a%20patentee%20only%20claims%20a%20particular%20process%20for%20manufacturing%20a%20particular%20product%20in%20its%20patent%20application%2C%20confining%20the%20scope%20of%20its%20patent%20to%20that%20process%20facilitates%20the%20manufacture%20of%20the%20same%20product%20by%20other%20processes%20by%20others%2C%20thus%20furthering%20the%20public%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%20public%20interest%2C%20as%20an%20extraneous%20consideration%2C%20can%20override%20well-settled%20legal%20principles%20for%20how%20a%20court%20should%20read%20the%20claims%20in%20a%20patent.%20It%20is%20just%20to%20say%20that%20public%20interest%20should%20be%20amongst%20the%20calculus%20of%20factors%20that%20an%20Indian%20court%20should%20consider%20when%20deciding%20which%20amongst%20multiple%20plausible%20arguments%20it%20should%20subscribe%20to%20when%20adjudicating%20patent%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20comprehensive%20and%20well-reasoned%20judgment%2C%20Justice%20Jyoti%20Singh%20of%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20began%20her%20analysis%20by%20making%20the%20perceptive%20observation%20that%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20light%20of%20the%20%5BAyyangar%5D%20report%2C%20one%20can%20safely%20state%20that%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20patent%20system%20is%20on%20an%20edifice%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbargaining%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20interest%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20means%20that%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20monopoly%20rights%20over%20the%20inventions%20disclosed%2C%20the%20patentee%20gets%20a%20protection%20over%20the%20invention%20for%20a%20limited%20term%20and%20in%20turn%20public%20stands%20to%20benefit%20by%20the%20disclosure%20of%20newer%20technologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20exhaustive%20evaluation%20of%20the%20material%20furnished%20by%20the%20plaintiff%20while%20applying%20for%20the%20patent%20over%20FCM%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20claims%20in%20the%20patent%20application%2C%20she%20concluded%20that%20the%20plaintiff%20had%20applied%20for%20a%20minutely%20detailed%20process%20for%20producing%20FCM%2C%20and%20not%20a%20patent%20for%20producing%20FCM%20per%20se.%20She%20therefore%20held%20that%20this%20was%20a%20product%20by%20process%20patent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20logical%20sequitur%20of%20this%20holding%20was%20that%20the%20defendant%20could%20be%20liable%20only%20if%20it%20used%20the%20patented%20process%20for%20manufacturing%20FCM.%20Since%20her%20finding%20was%20that%20this%20was%20not%20so%2C%20she%20held%20that%20the%20defendant%20was%20entitled%20to%20continue%20manufacturing%20the%20generic%20version%20of%20FCM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F29142658%2F5606166528_b12b9c251a_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22880%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F29142658%2F5606166528_b12b9c251a_b.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F29142658%2F5606166528_b12b9c251a_b-300x151.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFinal%20arguments%20on%20the%20matter%20commenced%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20September%204.%20Photo%3A%20Ramesh%20Lalwani%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY-2.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVifor%20challenged%20this%20decision%20before%20the%20Division%20Bench%20(DB)%2C%20which%20stayed%20Justice%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20judgment.%20It%20principally%20held%20that%20the%20defendants%20were%20unable%20to%20dislodge%20the%20claim%20of%20novelty%20on%20the%20plaintiff%E2%80%99s%20patent%20over%20FCM%20as%20a%20product%20or%20establish%20that%20FCM%20was%20discoverable%20from%20the%20prior%20art.%20It%20further%20held%20that%20one%20of%20the%20claims%20by%20the%20plaintiff%20was%20for%20a%20product%2C%20while%20the%20others%20were%20for%20a%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20basis%2C%20it%20disagreed%20with%20the%20holding%20that%20the%20patent%20in%20question%20was%20over%20a%20product%20by%20process.%20Dr%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20DB%E2%80%99s%20judgment%20which%20was%20dismissed%20on%20August%2022%2C%20as%20the%20high%20court%20had%20already%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20final%20arguments%20on%20September%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20DB%20hears%20final%20arguments%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20it%20is%20hoped%20that%20it%20will%20be%20alive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20what%20is%20at%20issue%20is%20not%20the%20novelty%20of%20Vifor%E2%80%99s%20patent%2C%20but%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%2C%20in%20substance%2C%20what%20Vifor%20was%20claiming%20was%20a%20patent%20over%20manufacturing%20FCM%20based%20on%20the%20process%20set%20out%20in%20its%20claims%20and%20not%20a%20monopoly%20over%20the%20manufacture%20of%20FCM%20per%20se.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20if%20the%20court%20finds%20that%20there%20are%20two%20plausible%20constructions%20of%20Vifor%E2%80%99s%20claims%2C%20one%20that%20would%20extend%20its%20monopoly%20to%20the%20product%20and%20the%20other%20that%20would%20keep%20it%20confined%20to%20the%20manufacture%20of%20FCM%20through%20the%20given%20process%2C%20let%20us%20hope%20that%20the%20court%20will%20have%20an%20eye%20to%20the%20public%20interest%20in%20promoting%20access%20to%20affordable%20medicines%20and%20the%20unique%20institutional%20context%20of%20modern%20Indian%20patent%20law%2C%20to%20which%20Justice%20Singh%20exhibited%20attentiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Bajaj%20is%20an%20Attorney%20at%20Ira%20Law%20and%20Yagya%20Kapoor%20is%20a%20fourth-year%20law%20student%20at%20the%20Vivekananda%20Institute%20for%20Professional%20Studies.%20Views%20are%20strictly%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693916128000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05164557%2FIntravenous-intravention.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fa-consequential-patent-struggle-vifor-msn-delhi-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20high%20court%20is%20hearing%20final%20arguments%20in%20a%20case%20where%20a%20company%20applied%20to%20patent%20one%20of%20its%20medicines.%20But%20does%20its%20application%20extend%20to%20the%20medicine%20itself%2C%20or%20just%20the%20process%20used%20to%20make%20it%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fa-consequential-patent-struggle-vifor-msn-delhi-hc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Chief%20of%20Army%2C%20M.M.%20Naravane%20Bats%20for%20Continued%2C%20Heavy%20Troop%20Deployment%20on%20Borders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F16113928%2Fpti.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20chief%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-indias-strategic-depth-is-of-little-value-from-pakistan-to-china-borders%2F1745319%2F%5C%22%3EM.M.%20Naravane%20has%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20was%20a%20need%20for%20India%20to%20not%20let%20up%20on%20heavy%20troop%20deployment%20on%20its%20borders.%20Naravane%2C%20who%20retired%20as%20army%20chief%20in%20April%202022%2C%20particularly%20cites%20religious%20centres%20close%20to%20the%20border%2C%20as%20reasons%20for%20his%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20opinion%20piece%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPrint%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Naravane%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CStrategic%20depth%20%E2%80%94%20the%20prevalence%20or%20absence%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20key%20determinant%20of%20a%20country%E2%80%99s%20National%20Security%20Strategy%E2%80%9D.%20He%20defines%20strategic%20depth%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20distance%20between%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20also%20called%20the%20Tactical%20Battle%20Area%20or%20TBA%2C%20and%20the%20base%2C%20from%20which%20the%20Army%20draws%20its%20strength%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20men%2C%20material%20and%20resources.%20The%20space%20in%20between%2C%20through%20which%20pass%20the%20roads%20and%20railroads%20connecting%20the%20two%2C%20the%20lines%20of%20communications%2C%20is%20known%20as%20the%20Communications%20Zone%20or%20Comn%20Z.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20a%20country%20has%20%E2%80%9Cneither%20the%20luxury%20of%20strategic%20depth%2C%20nor%20a%20friendly%20neighbour%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20depth%20has%20to%20be%20created%20by%20occupying%20territories%20beyond%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20boundaries.%20Israel%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%E2%80%9D%20On%20the%20six-day%20war%20of%201967%2C%20he%20compliments%20Israel%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Coccupation%20of%20the%20Sinai%20Peninsula%2C%20as%20it%20afforded%20them%20the%20depth%20against%20any%20surprise%20offensive%20by%20Egypt%20from%20the%20South.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20India%2C%20the%20former%20Army%20chief%20says%20that%20while%20it%20is%20blessed%20to%20have%20the%20advantage%20of%20a%20large%20land-mass%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmany%E2%80%A6lucrative%20targets%20also%20lie%20within%20or%20close%20to%20the%20TBA%20where%20they%20could%20be%20over-run%20in%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20an%20enemy%20offensive.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20has%20to%20carefully%20calibrate%20its%20strategy%20with%20respect%20to%20its%20potential%20adversaries%2C%20China%20to%20the%20North%20and%20Pakistan%20to%20the%20West.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifferent%20strokes%20for%20different%20folks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20Western%20Front%2C%20Naravane%20opines%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20desert%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20India%20could%20afford%20to%20be%20less%20densely%20deployed%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20inherent%20natural%20resources%2C%20especially%20water.%20However%2C%20the%20same%20would%20not%20be%20true%20further%20North.%E2%80%9D%20But%2C%20major%20population%20centres%20having%20political%20and%20religious%20significance%2C%20Amritsar%20for%20example%2C%20which%20is%20just%20about%2030%20plus%20kms%20from%20the%20international%20border%2C%20and%20well%20within%20the%20range%20of%20enemy%20long-range%20artillery%2C%20would%20have%20to%20be%20defended%20at%20all%20costs.%20Its%20fall%20would%20do%20irreparable%20damage%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20reputation%2C%20both%20domestically%20and%20internationally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20front%20with%20the%20Chinese%2C%20post%20the%20Galwan%20clash%20of%202020%2C%20both%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20and%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20Naravane%20notes%20with%20relief%2C%20have%20fortified%20their%20positions%20and%20are%20forward%20deployed%2C%20with%20neither%20side%20inclined%20to%20cede%20any%20space%20to%20the%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20central%20sector%2C%20bordering%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20lie%20places%20of%20religious%20importance%2C%20which%20once%20again%20have%20to%20be%20defended%20strongly%20right%20from%20the%20outset.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20for%20the%20Sikkim%20and%20Tawang%20areas%20of%20the%20eastern%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bottom%20line%2C%20he%20argues%20is%20that%20while%20India%20has%20a%20large%20landmass%2C%20its%20strategic%20depth%20is%20of%20little%20value%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20overriding%20domestic%20compulsions.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaravane%20ends%20on%20an%20enigmatic%20note%2C%20taking%20a%20line%20apparently%20contrary%20to%20what%20the%20political%20establishment%20and%20his%20successors%20have%20taken%20with%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagniveer-tour-of-duty-unemployment%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20Agniveer%20policy%20of%20hiring%20soldiers%20on%20short-term%20contracts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fresh%20recruitments%20in%20the%20Army%20were%20not%20done%20for%20years%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20citing%20COVID-19.%20The%20reason%20advanced%20for%20Tour%20of%20Duty%20or%20short%20term%20contractual%20soldiering%20was%20that%20%E2%80%98technological%20changes%E2%80%99%20make%20troops%20somewhat%20less%20necessary%20for%20battles%20in%20the%20future.%20But%2C%20says%20Naravane%2C%20without%20referring%20to%20Agniveer%20at%20all%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20spite%20of%20technological%20advances%2C%E2%80%9D%20deployment%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20northern%20fronts%20can%20only%20be%20done%20%E2%80%9Cby%20having%20adequate%20boots%20on%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693915255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F16113928%2Fpti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fex-chief-of-army-m-m-naravane-bats-for-continued-heavy-troop-deployment-on-borders%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20writes%20that%20while%20India%20has%20a%20large%20landmass%2C%20its%20strategic%20depth%20is%20of%20little%20value%20'due%20to%20overriding%20domestic%20compulsions.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fex-chief-of-army-m-m-naravane-bats-for-continued-heavy-troop-deployment-on-borders%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Challenge%20to%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20from%20a%20Radical%20Politics%20of%20Emancipation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05161929%2FF5MnpAzb0AAgIoy.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%202%2C%202023%2C%20when%20film%20actor%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%2C%20son%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20and%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20state%20government%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Ceradicate%E2%80%9D%20sanatana%20dharma%20during%20his%20talk%20at%20a%20Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conclave%20organised%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Progressive%20Writers%20and%20Artists%20Association%20in%20Chennai%2C%20his%20comment%20drew%20an%20immediate%20response%20of%20political%20outrage%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Udayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bs%5Dome%20things%20cannot%20be%20opposed%2C%20they%20should%20be%20eradicated%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20for%20which%20he%20gave%20the%20examples%20of%20dengue%2C%20malaria%20and%20Covid%2C%20adding%2C%20so%20should%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Amit%20Malviya%20hit%20out%20at%20him%20on%20social%20media.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Udayanidhi%20was%20calling%20for%20genocide%20of%2080%25%20population%20of%20Bharat.%20Home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20Udayanidhi%20had%20insulted%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cculture%2C%20history%20and%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20in%20Delhi%20an%20advocate%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police%20commissioner%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20comments%20presented%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdayanidhi%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20youth%20affairs%20and%20sports%20development%20portfolio%2C%20also%20reached%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUdhaystalin%2Fstatus%2F1698032382077800748%5C%22%3Ethrough%20posts%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20called%20for%20the%20genocide%20of%20people%20who%20are%20following%20sanatana%20dharma.%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20a%20principle%20that%20divides%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%20Uprooting%20sanatana%20dharma%20is%20upholding%20humanity%20and%20human%20equality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stated%20his%20position%20clearly%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20stand%20firmly%20by%20every%20word%20I%20have%20spoken.%20I%20spoke%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20oppressed%20and%20marginalised%2C%20who%20suffer%20due%20to%20the%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20present%20the%20extensive%20writings%20of%20Periyar%20and%20Ambedkar%2C%20who%20conducted%20in-depth%20research%20on%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20and%20its%20negative%20impact%20on%20society%20in%20any%20forum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20face%20any%20legal%20challenge%20that%20came%20his%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20has%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20political%20argument%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20level%20of%20the%20debate%20or%20articulation%20may%20be.%20In%20fact%2C%20by%20referring%20to%20E.V.%20Ramaswami%20Naicker%2C%20or%20Periyar%2C%20and%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20Udayanidhi%20was%20seeking%20to%20indicate%20the%20lineage%20of%20his%20views.%20But%20to%20understand%20this%20controversy%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20unpack%20the%20term%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fambedkar-periyar.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20faces%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20Periyar%20on%20a%20wall%20in%20Chennai.%20Credit%3A%20ferozfoto%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY-NC-SA%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22742%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-187524%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22525%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20faces%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20Periyar%20on%20a%20wall%20in%20Chennai.%20Credit%3A%20ferozfoto%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY-NC-SA%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanatana%20is%20an%20adjective%20meaning%20eternal%20or%20unchanging%2C%20often%20employed%20by%20those%20Hindus%20who%20view%20their%20faith%20as%20timeless%2C%20universal%20and%20immutable.%20To%20them%20it%20describes%20the%20essence%20or%20core%20of%20Hinduism%20as%20timeless%20and%20universal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHinduism%20is%20a%20modern%20term%20(from%20the%20early%2019th%C2%A0century)%20that%20accommodates%20a%20vast%20diversity%20of%20religious%20and%20cultural%20phenomena%20found%20across%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20single%20or%20unified%20religion%20but%20a%20collection%20of%20various%20sects%2C%20schools%2C%20philosophies%2C%20and%20traditions%20that%20share%20some%20common%20elements%20such%20as%20belief%20in%20reincarnation%2C%20karma%2C%20and%20the%20Vedas.%20Sanatana%20dharma%20and%20Hinduism%20are%20terms%20that%20are%20often%20used%20interchangeably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKim%20Knott%2C%20professor%20of%20religious%20and%20secular%20studies%20at%20Lancaster%20University%2C%20defines%20sanatana%20dharma%20in%20her%20book%20%3Cem%3EHinduism%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CMany%20describe%20Hinduism%20as%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20the%20eternal%20tradition%20or%20religion.%20This%20refers%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20its%20origins%20lie%20beyond%20human%20history%20and%20its%20truths%20have%20been%20divinely%20revealed%20(Shruti)%20and%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20ages%20to%20the%20present%20day%20in%20the%20most%20ancient%20of%20scriptures%2C%20the%20Vedas.%20Many%20share%20this%20faith%20perspective%20but%20varying%20opinions%20arise%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20interpreting%20human%20history%20in%20early%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20times%20sanatana%20dharma%20has%20been%20contested%20by%20social%20reformers%20and%20activists%20who%20have%20exposed%20the%20oppressive%20and%20discriminatory%20aspects%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20especially%20its%20caste%20system.%20Among%20them%2C%20two%20prominent%20figures%20stand%20out%3A%20Periyar%20and%20Ambedkar.%20Both%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ewere%20born%20in%20the%20late%2019th%20century%2C%20witnessed%20colonial%20rule%2C%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20and%20the%20post-independence%20era%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ebelonged%20to%20the%20so-called%20lower%20castes%3A%20Periyar%20was%20a%20non-Brahmin%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Ambedkar%20was%20from%20an%20oppressed%20caste%20from%20Maharashtra%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Echallenged%20the%20hegemony%20of%20Brahmins%20and%20upper%20castes%20in%20politics%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20religion%3B%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eadvocated%20the%20rights%20and%20dignity%20of%20the%20oppressed%20castes%2C%20especially%20the%20Shudras%20and%20the%20Dalits.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20both%20rejected%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20seeing%20it%20as%20the%20source%20of%20injustice%20and%20inequality%2C%20and%20both%20envisaged%20a%20society%20based%20on%20equality%2C%20the%20dignity%20of%20every%20individual%2C%20and%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeriyar%E2%80%99s%20critique%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeriyar%20was%20a%20radical%20social%20reformer%20who%20founded%20the%20Self-Respect%20Movement%20in%201925.%20%C2%A0Arguing%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20was%20used%20by%20Brahmins%20to%20exploit%20and%20oppress%20the%20lower%20castes%2C%20he%20denounced%20the%20concepts%20of%20karma%2C%20reincarnation%2C%20varna%2C%20dharma%2C%20and%20moksha%20as%20a%20means%20to%20justify%20the%20caste%20hierarchy%20and%20to%20keep%20the%20lower%20castes%20in%20perpetual%20servitude.%20To%20that%20end%2C%20Periyar%20challenged%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20Vedas%2C%20Upanishads%2C%20Puranas%20and%20Manusmriti%2C%20among%20others%2C%20saying%20those%20texts%20were%20the%20result%20of%20human%20output%2C%20and%20biased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERidiculing%20the%20myths%2C%20superstitions%2C%20and%20rituals%20that%20were%20considered%20part%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20he%20advocated%C2%A0%20a%20scientific%20temper%2C%20a%20rational%20outlook%2C%20and%20critical%20thinking%20among%20his%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeriyar%E2%80%99s%20critique%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20was%20not%20only%20intellectual%20but%20also%20political%20and%20cultural.%20He%20opposed%20the%20Brahminical%20influence%20in%20education%2C%20administration%2C%20media%2C%20literature%2C%20art%20and%20language%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20demanding%20equal%20rights%20and%20opportunities%20for%20all%20in%20every%20sphere%20of%20life.%20To%20secure%20this%20aim%2C%20Periyar%20supported%20social%20justice%20measures%20such%20as%20reservation%2C%20representation%2C%20education%20and%20empowerment%20for%20the%20so-called%20lower%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeriyar%20came%20to%20be%20known%20for%20his%20sharply%20articulated%20campaigns%20against%20caste%20discrimination%2C%20untouchability%2C%20child%20marriage%2C%20dowry%2C%20widowhood%2C%20polygamy%20and%20superstition.%20Promotion%20of%20gender%20equality%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20inter-caste%20marriage%2C%20birth%20control%20and%20family%20planning%20were%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20his%20lifelong%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20political%20level%2C%20he%20was%20strongly%20anti-imperialistic%20and%20anti-fascistic.%20He%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20Dravida%20ideology%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20which%20was%20based%20on%20several%20vital%20strands%3A%20championing%20of%20Tamil%20culture%20and%20calling%20for%20a%20Dravida%20nadu%2C%20opposition%20to%20Brahminism%2C%20and%20the%20domination%20of%20the%20north%20(in%20terms%20of%20Hindi%20or%20its%20Aryan%20culture)%20as%20exemplified%20by%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20The%20foundation%20of%20Dravidian%20politics%20was%20laid%20in%20the%201940s%20with%20the%20Dravida%20Kazhagam%20(when%20the%20Justice%20Party%20and%20the%20Self-Respect%20movement%20came%20together)%2C%20with%20political%20parties%20like%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20and%20All-India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(%20AIADMK)%20being%20later%20offshoots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20critique%20of%20dharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20strong%20trajectory%20of%20opposition%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20Hinduism%20as%20a%20sanatana%20dharma%20came%20from%20Baba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar.%20His%20own%20life%20exemplified%20the%20dehumanising%20aspect%20of%20caste%20society%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20being%20a%20brilliant%20scholar%2C%20lawyer%2C%20and%20leader%20he%20faced%20immense%20discrimination%20and%20humiliation%20due%20to%20his%20caste%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticulating%20that%20dharma%20was%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20his%20misery%20and%20that%20of%20millions%20of%20Dalits%2C%20especially%20the%20so-called%20untouchables%2C%20he%20argued%20that%20dharma%20was%20not%20eternal%20but%20historical%2C%20not%20universal%20but%20particular%2C%20not%20immutable%20but%20changeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20that%20Hinduism%20was%20not%20based%20on%20reason%2C%20morality%20or%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-648515%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20critique%20of%20Dharma%20was%20theoretical%20but%20also%20practical%20and%20legal.%20He%20fought%20for%20the%20civil%20and%20human%20rights%20of%20the%20marginalised%20and%20Dalits%20in%20various%20forums%20and%20platforms%2C%20leading%20movements%20and%20agitations%20such%20as%20the%20Mahad%20Satyagraha%20(to%20assert%20that%20%E2%80%98untouchables%E2%80%99%20had%20the%20right%20to%20access%20water%20in%20public%20places%2C%20and%20the%20Kalaram%20Temple%20Entry.%20%C2%A0We%20know%20him%20as%20the%20moving%20spirit%20behind%20the%20drafting%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Hindu%20Code%20Bill.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%2C%20his%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20entrenched%20inequality%20of%20the%20caste%20system%20was%20so%20acute%20that%20he%20renounced%20Hinduism%2C%20embracing%20Buddhism%20as%20the%20only%20way%20out%20for%20himself%20and%20his%20followers%20in%20the%20quest%20for%20human%20dignity%20and%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Periyar%20gave%20a%20call%20in%201922%20to%20renounce%20the%20Manusmriti%2C%20while%20Ambedkar%20burnt%20the%20Manusmriti%20in%201927%20during%20the%20Mahad%20satyagraha%2C%20to%20signify%20his%20rejection%20of%20the%20religious%20underpinning%20for%20untouchability.%20%C2%A0Periyar%20and%20Ambedkar%20were%20two%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20and%20radical%20thinkers%20and%20leaders%20of%20modern%20India.%20Their%20sharp%20critique%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20exposed%20the%20oppressive%20and%20discriminatory%20nature%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20its%20caste%20system%2C%20proposing%20alternative%20visions%20of%20society%20based%20on%20rationality%2C%20humanism%2C%20and%20democracy.%20In%20doing%20so%20they%20inspired%20generations%20of%20activists%20and%20spurred%20countless%20movements%20for%20social%20change%20and%20justice.%20Moreover%2C%20in%20the%20contemporary%20context%20of%20caste%20violence%2C%20communalism%2C%20and%20fascistic%20tone%20in%20dominant%20politics%2C%20the%20relevance%20of%20their%20ideas%20and%20quest%20remains%20undimmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fsanatana-dharma-remark-row-bjp-twisting-my-statement-says-tn-minister-udhayanidhi-stalin-11693794919192.html%5C%22%3EUdayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20query%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20Sanatana%3F%20Sanatana%20means%20nothing%20should%20be%20changed%20and%20all%20are%20permanent.%20But%20the%20Dravida%20model%20calls%20for%20change%20and%20all%20should%20be%20equal%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%C2%A0and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20him%20underscore%20one%20fact.%20Regardless%20the%20level%20of%20political%20discourse%20in%20our%20times%20and%20its%20purely%20instrumental%20nature%20(in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20salvos%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Udayanidhi%20reflecting%20the%20contestation%20between%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20DMK%20is%20part%20of)%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20this%20controversy%20has%20once%20again%20exposed%20a%20fundamental%20fault-line%20of%20Indian%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20also%20reveals%20that%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20when%20the%20dominant%20political%20project%20of%20our%20times%20is%20concerned%20with%20crafting%20an%20idea%20of%20Hinduism%20as%20a%20monolith%20and%20as%20a%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20ideas%20of%20towering%20figures%20like%20Periyar%20and%20Ambedkar%20is%20increasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Sandeep%20Yadav%20is%20a%20University%20Gold%20Medalist%20in%20PG.%20He%20has%20been%20teaching%20English%20as%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20in%20SLC(E)%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi%20for%20the%20last%2015%20years.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20permanent%20faculty%20member%20at%20the%20Central%20University%20of%20Jharkhand%20for%20four%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693913409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05161929%2FF5MnpAzb0AAgIoy.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-challenge-to-sanatana-dharma-from-a-radical-politics-of-emancipation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Udayanidhi%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20prepared%20to%20furnish%20the%20writings%20of%20Periyar%20and%20Ambedkar%20to%20defend%20his%20comments%20on%20sanatana%20dharma%20indicates%20the%20larger%20context%20of%20radical%2C%20anti-caste%20critiques%20of%20religion%20in%20India%2C%20then%20and%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-challenge-to-sanatana-dharma-from-a-radical-politics-of-emancipation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Xi's%20Refusal%20to%20Attend%20G20%20Marks%20Further%20Deterioration%20in%20Relations%2C%20Modi%20Must%20Be%20More%20Transparent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05162747%2FKT-5-Sep.00_39_10_08.Still002.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20Ambassadors%20to%20China%20Ashok%20Kantha%2C%20who%20is%20presently%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Institute%20of%20Chinese%20Studies%2C%20says%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20personally%20attend%20the%20G20%20summit%20on%20Saturday%20in%20Delhi%20marks%20a%20further%20deterioration%20in%20India-China%20relations.%20Although%20Kantha%20declined%20to%20call%20this%20a%20snub%2C%20he%20did%20say%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cessential%20messaging%E2%80%9D%20behind%20the%20Chinese%20president%E2%80%99s%20decision%20not%20to%20come%20to%20Delhi.%20Kantha%20said%20the%20message%20was%20that%20relations%20are%20in%20a%20downward%20spiral%20and%20there%20are%20no%20real%20prospects%20of%20improvement%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kantha%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20transparent%20and%20less%20opaque%20about%20the%20relationship%20with%20China.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20meeting%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20President%20Xi%20had%20in%20Johannesburg%20last%20month%20and%20the%20different%20versions%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20governments%2C%20Kantha%20accepted%20that%20these%20versions%20%E2%80%9Ccontradict%20each%20other%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20this%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdire%E2%80%9D%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKantha%20said%20that%20the%20differences%20and%20disagreements%20over%20the%20border%20are%20only%20one%20aspect%20of%20the%20problems%20affecting%20India-China%20relations.%20He%20said%20there%20are%20other%20structural%20concerns%2C%20including%20their%20different%20ways%20of%20seeing%20the%20world%2C%20the%20trade%20imbalance%20and%20China%E2%80%99s%20belief%20that%20India%20is%20ganging%20up%20against%20Beijing%2C%20which%20have%20not%20got%20the%20attention%20they%20need%20because%20the%20border%20dispute%20is%20the%20priority%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3