r%20their%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHanuman%2C%20secretary%20of%20Mamta%20Public%20School%2C%20found%20the%20project%20to%20be%20full%20of%20potential%2C%20notwithstanding%20a%20few%20challenges.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20importance%20of%20this%20project%20was%20to%20gain%20a%20first-hand%20understanding%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324007%2Fvadodara-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-vegetables-at-home-terrace-aquaponics-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20rooftop%20farming%20looks%20like%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20how%20it%20can%20help%2C%20with%20the%20intent%20that%20students%20learn%20something%20new%20and%20grow%20food%20on%20their%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20community%20members%20were%20always%20interested%20in%20farming%2C%C2%A0%20this%20project%20provided%20an%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%20take%20it%20up%20in%C2%A0%20their%20own%20homes.%20They%20found%20this%20to%20be%20a%20unique%20learning%20experience.%20Our%20students%2C%20too%2C%20were%20surprised%20to%20know%20that%20rooftops%20could%20be%20used%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20too.%20Of%20course%2C%20managing%20the%20rooftop%20space%20has%20its%20own%20challenges%3B%20the%20children%20sometimes%20wish%20to%20use%20the%20space%20for%20other%20purposes%20such%20as%20events%C2%A0%20and%20celebrations.%20Overall%2C%20I%20think%20the%20project%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20potential.%20An%20entire%20family%20of%20four%20can%20be%20fed%20with%20the%20harvest%20from%20the%20intervention.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ftree-planting-1693380807.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tree%20planting%20in%20jaipur%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2